Massive R&B is back for the Winter with a bigger and better album for all those current R&B lovers out there. The latest edition has 40 fresh hits including "When I Grow Up" (The Pussycat Dolls), "Miss Independent" (Ne-Yo), "Love in This Club (Usher), "Dance Wiv Me" (Dizzee Rascal), "Disturbia" (Rihanna) and "I Decided" (Solange Knowles) to name but a few.
